Subject: DC1 Scan Run time
Description: Sensitive data scans on DC1 is running for 6 days. Was previously running for 3+ hours.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Sensitive Data scans were taking days to complete

[Resolution]
We adjusted the below settings in the SEEK job xml:
Increased MAXTHREADS from 8 to 12
Increased MAXFOLDERTHREADS from 4 to 8
